headMarkup:
<style>
	.comm-page-login-home .salesforceIdentityLoginBody2 .cCenterPanel,
	.comm-page-forgot-password .salesforceIdentityLoginBody2 .cCenterPanel,
	.comm-page-check-password .salesforceIdentityLoginBody2 .cCenterPanel {
		max-width: 800px !important;
	}

	c-js-login-component input {
		height: 50px;
		background-color: rgb(103, 137, 138) !important;
		color: #ffffff !important;
	}

	c-js-login-component ::placeholder {
		/* Chrome, Firefox, Opera, Safari 10.1+ */
		color: #ffffff;
		opacity: 1; /* Firefox */
	}

	c-js-login-component :-ms-input-placeholder {
		/* Internet Explorer 10-11 */
		color: #ffffff;
	}

	c-js-login-component ::-ms-input-placeholder {
		/* Microsoft Edge */
		color: #ffffff;
	}

	c-js-login-component .slds-has-error .slds-form-element__help {
		color: #f5f5f5;
	}

	.comm-page-login-home .salesforceIdentityLoginBody2 .cCenterPanel,
	.comm-page-forgot-password .salesforceIdentityLoginBody2 .cCenterPanel,
	.comm-page-check-password .salesforceIdentityLoginBody2 .cCenterPanel {
		text-align: center !important;
		margin-top: 0% !important;
		margin-bottom: 0% !important;
	}

	.comm-page-login-home .salesforceIdentityLoginBody2 .cCenterPanel:before,
	.comm-page-forgot-password .salesforceIdentityLoginBody2 .cCenterPanel:before,
	.comm-page-check-password .salesforceIdentityLoginBody2 .cCenterPanel:before {
		display: none !important;
	}

	.comm-page-login-home .salesforceIdentityLoginBody2 .ui-widget,
	.comm-page-forgot-password .salesforceIdentityLoginBody2 .ui-widget,
	.comm-page-check-password .salesforceIdentityLoginBody2 .ui-widget {
		padding-top: 0px !important;
		padding-bottom: 0px !important;
	}

	c-pc-login-component .slds-has-error .slds-input,
	c-pc-login-component .slds-has-error .slds-input:focus,
	c-pc-login-component .slds-has-error .slds-input:active {
		border-color: rgb(241 208 70);
		box-shadow: rgb(241 208 70) 0 0 0 1px inset;
	}

	.loginButton {
		background-color: #c2e3cc !important;
		color: #054547 !important;
		font-size: 16px !important;
		line-height: 2 !important;
		font-weight: 600 !important;
		border-radius: none !important;
		margin-top: 0px !important;
		margin-bottom: 0px !important;
	}

	.loginButton .label {
		color: #054547 !important;
	}

	launchpad-pc-login-component .slds-spinner_container {
		background-color: unset !important;
	}

	.comm-page-self-register .salesforceIdentityLoginBody2 {
		background-color: #ffffff;
	}

	.comm-page-self-register .salesforceIdentityLoginBody2 .cCenterPanel .contentRegion {
		padding: 0px;
	}

	.comm-page-self-register .salesforceIdentityLoginBody2 .cCenterPanel {
		top: 0 !important;
		width: 100% !important;
		position: fixed !important;
		margin: 0;
		max-width: 100%;
	}

	@media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
		.comm-page-self-register lightning-button button.slds-button {
			height: 52px !important;
		}

		.comm-page-self-register .slds-is-absolute {
			position: fixed !important;
		}

		.comm-page-self-register input[type='date'] {
			width: 345px !important;
		}

		.comm-page-custom-my-profile input[type='date'] {
			width: 300px !important;
		}

		.comm-page-custom-my-profile launchpad-resume-builder input[type='date'] {
			width: 260px !important;
		}

		.comm-page-custom-my-profile launchpad-common-intake input[type='date'] {
			width: 275px !important;
		}

		.comm-page-custom-skills-building input[type='date'] {
			width: 280px !important;
		}

		.comm-page-custom-special-programs .comm-layout-column h1.header {
			font-size: 38px !important;
		}

		.comm-page-custom-special-programs .comm-layout-column p.description {
			font-size: 14px !important;
		}

		.comm-page-custom-special-programs .comm-layout-column .bodyMobile {
			padding: 0px !important;
		}

		.comm-page-custom-special-programs .comm-layout-column .gridBodyMobile {
			padding: 1.5rem 0px !important;
			margin: 0px;
		}

		.forceMobileOverlay .uiButton--brand {
			background-color: #054547 !important;
			border-color: #054547 !important;
			padding: 0 1rem !important;
			color: #ffffff !important;
		}

		.forceMobileOverlay .panel-header {
			padding: 1rem !important;
		}
	}

	.comm-page-self-register .salesforceIdentityLoginBody2:before,
	.comm-page-self-register .salesforceIdentityLoginBody2 .cCenterPanel:before {
		display: none;
	}

	.comm-page-self-register .salesforceIdentityLoginBody2 .cHeaderPanel .ui-widget,
	.comm-page-custom-my-profile .salesforceIdentityLoginBody2 .cHeaderPanel .ui-widget {
		padding: 0px !important;
	}

	.comm-page-self-register input,
	.comm-page-custom-my-profile input {
		height: 42px !important;
	}

	@media only screen and (min-width: 600px) {
		.comm-page-self-register lightning-button button.slds-button {
			height: 42px !important;
		}
	}

	.slds-notify_toast,
	.slds-notify--toast {
		min-width: unset !important;
	}

	.comm-page-self-register .slds-has-error .slds-input,
	.comm-page-self-register .slds-has-error .slds-textarea,
	.comm-page-custom-my-profile .slds-has-error .slds-input,
	.comm-page-custom-my-profile .slds-has-error .slds-textarea {
		box-shadow: none !important;
		color: var(--sds-c-input-text-color);
		background-clip: none !important;
		border: 1px solid rgb(212, 212, 212) !important;
		background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255) !important;
	}

	.comm-page-self-register lightning-input[type='date'],
	.comm-page-custom-my-profile .myProfile lightning-input,
	.comm-page-custom-my-profile .myProfile lightning-input[type='date'] {
		width: 100% !important;
	}

	.comm-page-self-register lightning-input.customError,
	.comm-page-custom-my-profile lightning-input.customError {
		width: 90% !important;
	}

	.comm-page-self-register div.customError + lightning-icon.error,
	.comm-page-self-register div:not(.customError) + lightning-icon.error + div.success,
	.comm-page-self-register div.customError > .requiredError,

	.comm-page-custom-my-profile div:not(.customError) + lightning-icon.error + div.success,
	.comm-page-custom-my-profile div.customError > .requiredError {
		display: unset !important;
	}

	.comm-page-self-register div.customError > .requiredError,
	.comm-page-custom-my-profile div.customError > .requiredError {
		color: rgb(234, 0, 30);
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		margin-top: 0.125rem;
		display: block;
	}

	.comm-page-self-register div:not(.customError) + lightning-icon.error,
	.comm-page-self-register div.customError + lightning-icon.error + div.success,
	.comm-page-self-register div:not(.customError) > .requiredError,

	.comm-page-self-register lightning-dual-listbox.slds-has-error .slds-form-element__help,
	.comm-page-custom-my-profile div:not(.customError) + lightning-icon.error,
	.comm-page-custom-my-profile div.customError + lightning-icon.error + div.success,
	.comm-page-custom-my-profile div:not(.customError) > .requiredError,
	.comm-page-custom-my-profile lightning-input label abbr,
	.comm-page-custom-my-profile lightning-dual-listbox.slds-has-error .slds-form-element__help {
		display: none !important;
	}

	.comm-page-self-register lightning-input label,
	.comm-page-custom-my-profile lightning-input label {
		font-size: 15px;
	}

	.comm-page-self-register launchpad-pc-self-registration-body {
		height: calc(100% - 100px);
		overflow-y: scroll;
		position: fixed;
		width: 100%;
	}

	.comm-page-self-register u > a,
	.comm-page-self-register u > a:hover,
	.comm-page-self-register .mobileFooterCSS a,
	.comm-page-self-register .mobileFooterCSS a:hover {
		color: #ffffff !important;
	}

	.comm-page-login-home .salesforceIdentityLoginBody2 .cCenterPanel .footer a,
	.comm-page-forgot-password .salesforceIdentityLoginBody2 .cCenterPanel .footer a,
	.comm-page-check-password .salesforceIdentityLoginBody2 .cCenterPanel .footer a,
	.comm-page-login-home .salesforceIdentityLoginBody2 .cCenterPanel .footer a:hover,
	.comm-page-forgot-password .salesforceIdentityLoginBody2 .cCenterPanel .footer a:hover,
	.comm-page-check-password .salesforceIdentityLoginBody2 .cCenterPanel .footer a:hover {
		color: #c2e3cc !important;
	}

	.comm-page-self-register .slds-listbox_vertical .slds-listbox__option:focus,
	.comm-page-self-register .slds-listbox_vertical .slds-listbox__option:hover,
	.comm-page-self-register .slds-listbox_vertical .slds-listbox__option.slds-has-focus,

	.comm-page-custom-my-profile .slds-listbox--vertical .slds-listbox__option:hover,

		color: #ffffff !important;
		text-decoration: none;
	}

		display: none !important;
	}

	.forceCommunityThemeProfileMenu.emberInnerHeader .profile-menuTrigger .profile-name {
		color: rgb(84, 105, 141) !important;
		text-shadow: 0 0 4px rgb(0 0 0 / 0%);
	}

	.comm-page-custom-special-programs .comm-layout-column {
		padding: 0px !important;
	}

	.comm-page-custom-special-programs .comm-layout-column h1.header {
		font-size: 70px;
	}

	.comm-page-custom-special-programs .comm-layout-column p.description {
		font-size: 20px;
	}
    
    /* Start of fixing lightning-map overflow bug */
    .slds-map-container {
        height: 80vh !important;
    }
    
    .slds-has-coordinates {
        overflow: hidden;
        max-height: none !important;
    }
    
    .slds-coordinates {
        height: 80vh !important;
    }
    
    .slds-coordinates__list {
        max-height: calc(100% - 56px) !important;
        overflow: auto;
    }
    /* End of fixing lightning-map overflow bug */
</style>
label: main
